here backstage at Cort Romney's show.

894
01:03:49,872 --> 01:03:54,501
Isabella de la Fontaine has fainted.
She has lost consciousness.

895
01:03:54,668 --> 01:03:58,213
- Her condition--
Is she dead? Is she dead?
- [Man] No, she's okay.

896
01:03:58,380 --> 01:04:01,466
