rocked the fashion world...

918
01:05:09,910 --> 01:05:13,747
by taking her husband's
symbolically vacant seat...

919
01:05:13,914 --> 01:05:17,417
in the front row, wearing what fashion
observers could only speculate to be...

920
01:05:17,584 --> 01:05:19,878
a vintage Dior dress,
we think.

921
01:05:20,045 --> 01:05:21,880
Until his untimely death...

922
01:05:22,047 --> 01:05:24,883
Olivier de la Fontaine
was commonly known to be involved...

923
01:05:25,050 --> 01:05:27,261
with Simone Lowenthal for most
of his duration through the marriage.

924
01:05:27,427 --> 01:05:29,263
Oh, here she is!
She's lookin' mighty fine to me.

925
01:05:29,429 --> 01:05:31,265
Hello!
Who made your dress?

926
01:05:48,991 --> 01:05:50,826
Very nice accessory.

927
01:05:50,993 --> 01:05:52,828
Yes, this is very good.

928
01:05:55,455 --> 01:05:58,667
No. He doesn't even suspect,
but he's such a bitch.

929
