949
01:07:28,006 --> 01:07:31,552
Anyway, tell me your-- your ideas
on beauty, would you please?

950
01:07:31,718 --> 01:07:34,012
[French Accent] I think there is
not only one idea of beauty.

951
01:07:34,179 --> 01:07:36,390
